'''Baruch Spinoza''', yettwassen daɣen s yisem n ''Bento de Espinosa'' neɣ ''Benedictus de Spinoza'', ilul ass n {{azmez|24|Wamber|1632}} di Amsterdam, yemmut ass n  {{azmez|21|Fuṛaṛ|1677}} di [[Den Haag]]. Yella d amesnagay n [[Tamurt n Wadda|Tmurt n Wadda]] uɣur tasnezgimt tesɛa tazrirt s wazal-is ɣef waziten n tillit dgi yedder d waṭas n wid it-id-iḍefṛen.

